== 製作 ==
2018年11月26日，據報導《[[包寶寶|包寶寶]]》的編劇和導演[[石之予|石之予]]將執導一部皮克斯長篇電影，使她成為皮克斯第一個有色人種女導演<ref>{{cite web|last=Grobar|first=Matt|url=https://deadline.com/2018/11/bao-domee-shi-pixar-oscars-animation-interview-1202508540/|title=The First Woman To Direct An Oscar-Contending Pixar Short, ‘Bao’s Domee Shi Is On Her Way To First Feature Project|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2018-11-26|accessdate=2020-12-11|archive-date=2020-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217154159/https://deadline.com/2018/11/bao-domee-shi-pixar-oscars-animation-interview-1202508540/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年12月10日，[[皮克斯動畫工作室|皮克斯動畫工作室]]在迪士尼投資者日上正式宣佈正在製作一部有關青春期女孩的電影，由石之予執導，琳賽·柯林斯擔任製片人，並預定於2022年3月11日上映<ref>{{cite web|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|url=https://deadline.com/2020/12/pixar-has-buzz-lightyear-movie-in-the-works-with-chris-evans-turning-red-from-bao-filmmaker-domee-shi-1234654489/|title=Pixar Has Buzz Lightyear Origin Movie In Works With Chris Evans & ‘Turning Red’ From ‘Bao’ Filmmaker Domee Shi|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2020-12-10|accessdate=2020-12-11|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125164218/https://deadline.com/2020/12/pixar-has-buzz-lightyear-movie-in-the-works-with-chris-evans-turning-red-from-bao-filmmaker-domee-shi-1234654489/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Hermanns|first=Grant|url=https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/1157891-pixar-unveils-new-coming-of-age-2022-comedy-turning-red|title=Pixar Unveils New Coming-Of-Age 2022 Comedy Turning Red!|publisher=Comingsoon.net|date=2020-12-10|accessdate=2020-12-11|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225115927/https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/1157891-pixar-unveils-new-coming-of-age-2022-comedy-turning-red|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年7月13日，釋出前導預告片，並宣佈[[姜晋安|姜晋安]]和[[吳珊卓|吳珊卓]]加入主要配音陣容<ref>{{cite web|last=Sharf|first=Zack|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2021/07/turning-red-trailer-pixar-1234650740/|title=‘Turning Red’ First Trailer: Pixar Unleashes a Beast in New Film from ‘Bao’ Oscar Winner|publisher=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|date=2021-07-08|accessdate=2021-07-08|archive-date=2021-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210920223003/https://www.indiewire.com/2021/07/turning-red-trailer-pixar-1234650740/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

