== 主題 ==
多数影评人指出，《青春養成記》涉及的主题含括[[青春期|青春期]]、家庭、友谊、接纳真实自我的成长蜕变<ref name="Washington Post">{{Cite news |last=O'Sullivan |first=Michael |title=Pixar's 'Turning Red' is a brilliant, hilarious follow-up to Oscar-winning short 'Bao' |newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/movies/2022/03/09/turning-red-movie-review/ |url-status=live |access-date=2022-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220313161522/https://www.washingtonpost.com/movies/2022/03/09/turning-red-movie-review/ |archive-date=2022-03-13 |issn=}}</ref><ref name="IGN">{{cite web |last=Adlakha |first=Siddhant |date=2022-03-07 |title=Turning Red Review |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/turning-red-review |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220314012050/https://www.ign.com/articles/turning-red-review |archive-date=2022-03-14 |access-date=2022-03-14 |website=[[IGN|IGN]]}}</ref>。《[[英国广播公司新闻网|英国广播公司新闻网]]》的尼可拉斯·巴勃尔（{{lang-en|Nicholas Barber}}）在影评裡称，发现自己变成红熊猫的美玲躲在[[浴室|浴室]]裡，对她新生的腋毛和体味感到厌恶，隐晦地暗示青春期的变化<ref name="BBC.com">{{cite web |last=Barber |first=Nicholas |date=2022-03-07 |title=Turning Red Review |url=https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20220307-turning-red-review-hilarious-life-affirming-new-pixar|url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20220307-turning-red-review-hilarious-life-affirming-new-pixar |archive-date=2022-03-07 |access-date=2022-03-07 |website=[[英国广播公司新闻网|英国广播公司新闻网]]}}</ref>。

尼可拉斯·巴勃尔对剧中隐喻青春期的解读和《{{link-en|FOX 10|KSAZ-TV}}》的卡洛琳·赛迪（{{lang-en|Caroline Siede}}）在文章裡谈及青春期的观点相同<ref name="FOX 10">{{cite web |last=Siede |first=Caroline |date=2022-03-12 |title=Review:‘Turning Red’ is Pixar at its weird, wonderful best|url=https://www.fox10phoenix.com/news/review-turning-red-is-pixar-at-its-weird-wonderful-best|url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.fox10phoenix.com/news/review-turning-red-is-pixar-at-its-weird-wonderful-best|archive-date=2022-03-12 |access-date=2022-03-12 |website=FOX 10 PHOENIX}}</ref>。卡洛琳·赛迪在影评裡更进一步谈道，美玲和父母关係关係良好，但有时候会在她的校园生活和对于过度保护、以家庭为中心的母亲明之间的关係感到痛苦，同时美玲开始在家庭之外培养兴趣，努力与一个显然更愿意让女儿维持不变的妈妈平衡这一点<ref name="FOX 10">{{cite web |last=Siede |first=Caroline |date=2022-03-12 |title=Review:‘Turning Red’ is Pixar at its weird, wonderful best|url=https://www.fox10phoenix.com/news/review-turning-red-is-pixar-at-its-weird-wonderful-best|url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.fox10phoenix.com/news/review-turning-red-is-pixar-at-its-weird-wonderful-best|archive-date=2022-03-12 |access-date=2022-03-12 |website=FOX 10 PHOENIX}}</ref>。她认为《青春养成记》同样是关于成长和在家庭之外塑造自己的身份、所带来的更广泛的情感动盪，着眼于作为一个补述女孩成长过程中復杂的情感现实，像是和《[[脑筋急转弯_(电影)|脑筋急转弯]]》相辅相成的作品，但它同样让人感觉像是《[[勇敢传说|勇敢传说]]》的精神续集<ref name="FOX 10">{{cite web |last=Siede |first=Caroline |date=2022-03-12 |title=Review:‘Turning Red’ is Pixar at its weird, wonderful best|url=https://www.fox10phoenix.com/news/review-turning-red-is-pixar-at-its-weird-wonderful-best|url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.fox10phoenix.com/news/review-turning-red-is-pixar-at-its-weird-wonderful-best|archive-date=2022-03-12 |access-date=2022-03-12 |website=FOX 10 PHOENIX}}</ref>，写道美玲的变身与她的情绪起伏有关，但是健康的管理情绪和不健康地否认情绪变得无异，尤其是身处在一个不公平期待人们待在框架裡的世界<ref name="FOX 10">{{cite web |last=Siede |first=Caroline |date=2022-03-12 |title=Review:‘Turning Red’ is Pixar at its weird, wonderful best|url=https://www.fox10phoenix.com/news/review-turning-red-is-pixar-at-its-weird-wonderful-best|url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.fox10phoenix.com/news/review-turning-red-is-pixar-at-its-weird-wonderful-best|archive-date=2022-03-12 |access-date=2022-03-12 |website=FOX 10 PHOENIX}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《熊抱青春記》原定於2022年3月11日在美國院線上映<ref>{{cite web|last=Lattanzio|first=Ryan|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/12/new-pixar-movies-revealed-disney-investor-day-1234603833/|title=Pixar Announces Buzz Lightyear Movie with the Voice of Chris Evans|publisher=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|date=2020-12-10|accessdate=2020-12-11|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211003918/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/12/new-pixar-movies-revealed-disney-investor-day-1234603833/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2022年1月，受[[嚴重急性呼吸道症候群冠狀病毒2型Omicron變異株|嚴重急性呼吸道症候群冠狀病毒2型Omicron變異株]]影響，迪士尼宣佈該片將與《[[靈魂急轉彎|靈魂急轉彎]]》和《[[路卡的夏天|路卡的夏天]]》一樣直接上線[[Disney+|Disney+]]，而沒有Disney+的地區則維持院線上映<ref>{{cite web |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |title=Pixar's 'Turning Red' Skips Theaters & Heads To Disney+ |url=https://deadline.com/2022/01/turning-red-skips-theaters-disney-premiere-1234906438/ |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |date=2022-01-07 |access-date=2022-01-07 |archive-date=2022-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220108021845/https://deadline.com/2022/01/turning-red-skips-theaters-disney-premiere-1234906438/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。受[[2022年俄乌军事冲突|2022年俄乌军事冲突]]影响，迪士尼决定不在俄罗斯发行影片<ref>{{cite web |last1=McClintock |first1=Pamela |last2=Couch |first2=Aaron |date=2022-02-28 |title=Disney First Hollywood Studio to Pause Theatrical Releases in Russia |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/disney-russia-theatrical-releases-1235101526/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220301052659/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/disney-russia-theatrical-releases-1235101526/ |archive-date=2022-03-01 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |access-date=2022-02-28}}</ref>。

== 评价 ==
[[汇总媒体|汇总媒体]][[烂番茄|烂番茄]]收录259条评论，新鲜度94%，平均得分8/10。网站共识写道：“《青春变形记》温暖、幽默、画风精美、文化底蕴深厚，让皮克斯长久以来的合家欢精品再添一笔<ref>{{cite web |title=Turning Red |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/turning_red |website=Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=Fandango Media |accessdate=2022-04-15}}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]收录52条评论，平均得分83/100<ref>{{cite web |title=Turning Red |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/turning-red-2022 |website=Metacritic |publisher=Red Ventures |accessdate=2022-04-15}}</ref>。

影片首轮点映结束后，影评人认可影片的剧情、配音及石之予的执导工作<ref>{{cite web |last=Labonte |first=Rachel |date=2022-02-22 |title=Early Turning Red Reactions Praise Pixar's Coming of Age Movie |url=https://screenrant.com/turning-red-movie-early-reactions-reviews |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220227142759/https://screenrant.com/turning-red-movie-early-reactions-reviews/ |archive-date=2022-02-27 |access-date=2022-03-03 |website=Screen Rant}}</ref>。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的迈克尔·奥沙利文（Michael O'Sullivan） 给予4颗星的佳评，称这部电影表达出更大、更广泛的普世讯息：「不让事情总是落在掌控范围之中是好的，可以展现个人独特的一面。」，解释若对[[西格蒙德·弗洛伊德|西格蒙德·弗洛伊德]]作出释义，红熊猫便只是红熊猫，有时候这隐喻着内在的创造力火花，个人独创性的光芒应该被加以珍惜，不是将它熄灭；石之予则针对本片证明她理解许多层面<ref name="Washington Post">{{Cite news |last=O'Sullivan |first=Michael |title=Pixar's 'Turning Red' is a brilliant, hilarious follow-up to Oscar-winning short 'Bao' |newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/movies/2022/03/09/turning-red-movie-review/ |url-status=live |access-date=2022-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220313161522/https://www.washingtonpost.com/movies/2022/03/09/turning-red-movie-review/ |archive-date=2022-03-13 |issn=}}</ref>。《[[卫报|卫报]]》的班杰明·李（Benjamin Lee） 给予本片三颗星（满分五颗星）的评比分数，评论此片「这是趟花俏且令人转移注意力，同时鞭闢入裡的旅程，但是《青春养成记》并不是一部游走在边缘的皮克斯电影，希望次回的作品能转变成更为珍贵的事物」<ref>{{cite web |last=Lee |first=Benjamin |date=2022-03-07 |title=Turning Red review – pandas and pop music collide in solid Pixar caper |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2022/mar/07/turning-red-review-pandas-and-pop-music-collide-in-solid-pixar-caper |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220313152216/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2022/mar/07/turning-red-review-pandas-and-pop-music-collide-in-solid-pixar-caper |archive-date=2022-03-13 |access-date=2022-03-14 |website=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]}}</ref>。《[[IGN|IGN]]》的席德杭特·阿拉克哈（Siddhant Adlakha）给予本片超过9颗星（满分10颗星）的高度评价，说道：「作为用魔法变形比喻个人和文化转变的故事，《青春养成记》是皮克斯年度最有趣且最富想像力的电影，不仅捕捉青春期的野性能量，使用流行艺人作为窥探青春期的无时限视角，还用愉悦且友善的方式诉说有关家庭和友谊的故事。」<ref name="IGN">{{cite web |last=Adlakha |first=Siddhant |date=2022-03-07 |title=Turning Red Review |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/turning-red-review |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220314012050/https://www.ign.com/articles/turning-red-review |archive-date=2022-03-14 |access-date=2022-03-14 |website=[[IGN|IGN]]}}</ref> 除了加拿大的华裔观众以外，该片亦获得[[韩国|韩国]]、南亚区域的观众好评<ref>{{Cite web |last=Schweitzer |first=Kate |date=2021-07-22 |title=Blink and You'll Miss the Diabetic Kid in Pixar's Turning Red Trailer, but It Left a Major Impact on Fans |url=https://www.popsugar.com/node/48429698 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220319111549/https://www.popsugar.com/family/pixar-turning-red-features-character-with-diabetes-48429698 |archive-date=2022-03-19 |access-date=2022-03-21 |website=[[PopSugar|PopSugar]] |language=en-US}}</ref>。

《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的理查·罗伊柏（Richard Roeper）在满分四颗星的评分标准裡给本片两颗半星，写道：「这部电影的主要问题，出在总是需要美玲激发愤怒可憎的脚本上，而且她的母亲在整篇故事裡的表现像是头怪兽，取用不断增加的超自然元素向《[[魔鬼剋星系列|魔鬼剋星系列]]》致敬。」<ref>{{Cite web |last=Roeper |first=Richard |date=2022-03-09 |title=‘Turning Red’: Our little girl is becoming a ... panda? |url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/movies-and-tv/2022/3/9/22967167/turning-red-review-disney-pixar-movie-billie-eilish-finnian |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220320091258/https://chicago.suntimes.com/movies-and-tv/2022/3/9/22967167/turning-red-review-disney-pixar-movie-billie-eilish-finnian |archive-date=2022-03-20 |access-date=2022-03-29 |website=[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]] |language=en}}</ref>。

