ailybeast.com/how-did-pixars-delightful-turning-red-become-the-target-of-sexist-racist-controversy?ref=home |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220317074401/https://www.thedailybeast.com/how-did-pixars-delightful-turning-red-become-the-target-of-sexist-racist-controversy |archive-date=2022-03-17 |work=[[The_Daily_Beast|The Daily Beast]] |accessdate=March 16, 2022}}</ref>。

